(26, '修改数据库默认密码后phpmyadmin无法连接的问题', '', '<p>修改数据库默认密码后phpmyadmin无法连接，提示phpMyAdmin 试图连接到 MySQL 服务器，但服务器拒绝连接</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://i2.cfimg.com/604780/a659b3ef4134a3ec.png\" alt=\"Markdown\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>解决方案</strong></p>\r\n<p>在phpMyAdmin的安装目录下找到配置文件 config.inc.php </p>\r\n<p>修改其中的密码项$cfg[‘Servers’][$i][‘password’]就可以了</p>\r\n<pre><code>/* Authentication type and info */\r\n$cfg[\'Servers\'][$i][\'auth_type\'] = \'config\';\r\n$cfg[\'Servers\'][$i][\'user\'] = \'用户名\';\r\n$cfg[\'Servers\'][$i][\'password\'] = \'密码\';\r\n$cfg[\'Servers\'][$i][\'extension\'] = \'mysqli\';\r\n$cfg[\'Servers\'][$i][\'AllowNoPassword\'] = true;\r\n$cfg[\'Lang\'] = \'\';\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n', 14, 1509285458201, 'mysql,密码,phpmyadmin,无法连接');
